trans-unit.target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICE<tab>Hope, is it...? Futile. Utterly futile. Such feeble light is powerless before darkest despair.
